Define and Use Index Aliases
Use the _aliases API to add or remove aliases with:
POST _aliases
{
"actions": [
{
"add": {. # add an alias
"index": "", # index name or pattern
"alias": "", # the alias to add
"filter": { ... } # filtered alias
}
},
{
"remove": { # removes an alias
"index": "", # index name or pattern
"alias": "" # alias to remove
}
},}
}
